    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. The primary validation activity demonstrates RH < 1.0 for all five CPB operating points against the Graefe et al. (2022) hemolysis dataset, which the team considers a relevant and high-quality comparator on account of geometric and fluid-property similarity. The credibility assessment is accepted and the CFD model is judged adequate for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device as declared in the COU.",
